{"tid":961671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"防守差過雲加同期 艾美利求改善","createTime":"2018-12-30T10:02:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T06:16:44.000Z","uid":1121,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"425b2907238d24c45d8cd6e7cd1e9b1d801da7d0","tid":961671,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:02:38.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=y7SzFf8rwXZQ0WRSkoCQ%2B3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5587e3ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】說雲加時代防守差？原來沒有最差只有更差。周六英超尾場，阿仙奴作客遭利物浦血洗5:1，本季迄今失球數都高於前帥雲加同期，艾美利坦言要改善防守。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴雖然先開紀錄，最終卻被利物浦大炒5:1，艾美利（Unai Emery）自然失望：「我們開局表現不錯，取得第1個入球，之後他們在進攻上以決心及質素，創造出不同，我們未能阻止他們。」<br />\n<br />\n就算半場已經遙遙落後1:4，但艾美利表示在下半場從未放棄：「我們在下半場希望一點一點地提升表現，找到更多入球，另一個12碼卻終結了比賽。這是一個很差的戰果，但我們可以好好利用。」<br />\n<br />\n兵工廠今季攻強守弱，今場再失5球後，20場英超合共失達30球，這是雲加時代同期不曾錄過的失球數字，就是去季的「末代」亦只是25球。<br />\n<br />\n艾美利續說：「我們知道要改善防守。利物浦進步很多，是己隊的榜樣，我們一定要進步。」榜首紅軍20場僅失8球，幾乎是阿仙奴的四份之一。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F1xopmJv5fWPtUSZ8Hh%2Fgiphy.gif&h=35d21f9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"62f44f5cc7328b85778dad33e35c4d4752a58d8c","tid":961671,"uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:03:04.000Z","msg":"反雲必需悔改"},{"pid":"236258b1b1b58b2a7608e990a486f4f776f3a20f","tid":961671,"uid":1121,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/SpotlessJitteryBluebottle-max-1mb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FSpotlessJitteryBluebottle-max-1mb.gif&h=edc28c5d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e8d376423098b006df1ca43a0e34d239e4af62b","tid":961671,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:07:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98730dfc6ce73cb5f5c78675b5af3c72f2737b68","tid":961671,"uid":30768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"躝啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"14137b7fd56598193af5b2b87dbc5aeec0dc3815","tid":961671,"uid":220634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T14:54:44.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺快回來"},{"pid":"cd58d78ef71839988702fa32aa99c5491ef63d98","tid":961671,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98730dfc6ce73cb5f5c78675b5af3c72f2737b68","tid":961671,"uid":30768,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"躝啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"你話who"},{"pid":"66c30d43bfc93afa2af3fa92472fcef940a3fca9","tid":961671,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"雲加又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}